<pre><code>&lt;div id="askfriend"&gt;       &lt;form action="friend.php" method="post"&gt;        &lt;input type="submit" id="requestbutton" name="requestbutton2" value="Send Friend Request" style="margin-top:5%; margin-left:10%; height:50%;" onclick="change()"/&gt;        &lt;input type="submit" id="cancelbutton" name="cancelbutton2" value="Cancel" disabled style="margin-top:5%; margin-left:10%; height:50%; width:30%;" onclick="changeback()"/&gt;       &lt;/form&gt;        &lt;?php         if(isset($_POST['requestbutton2']))          {           echo "clicked";          }        ?&gt;      &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;script&gt;   function change()    {     var elem=document.getElementById("requestbutton");     var elem2=document.getElementById("cancelbutton");     if(elem.value=="Send Friend Request")      {       elem.value="Friend Request Send";       elem.disabled=true;       elem2.disabled=false;      }    }   function changeback()    {     var elem=document.getElementById("requestbutton");     var elem2=document.getElementById("cancelbutton");     if(elem2.value=="Cancel")      {       elem2.disabled=true;       elem.value="Send Friend Request";       elem.disabled=false;        }    }  &lt;/script&gt; </code></pre>  <p>when I click "Send Friend Request" button javascript code runs but the action code whatever I wrote inside php, for the same button does not run. What's the solution?</p>